1.title: Fast and Furious 7th Edition

episode of.title: Michael & Yossi: Rated or Dated (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: Michael rips apart Fast and Furious 7. Raising the question of whether the hype around the film was justified, and whether it was actually any good as a film. Yossi and Singer-songwriter Thomas Fowkes sit in silence, later confessing that they had never had time to watch the Fast and Furious anthology.
